name: pick & Mixx - All nails available in stiletto shape
description:
Hand-painted nails exclusively designed by BinBagCouture . Sets come with 12 various sized nails in a protective pouch for longer wear. 

Each purchase includes a set of 12 false nails, each individually hand painted and sealed with a top coat. There are different sizes and larger nails can easily be filed to fit. The nails may vary slightly from the pictures because they're all hand painted. The nails can be reapplied and worn more than once.

*Adhesive is not included*

Feel free to email me if you have any questions or custom requests x
